PRECAUTION
The new (v1.1.1) fluxbox binary will convert your 'old' ~/.fluxbox/*-files as
necessary during its first startup. If you want the root-menu to appear if you
right-click the desktop make sure to add the following lines to your
~/.fluxbox/keys:

OnDesktop Mouse1 :hideMenus
OnDesktop Mouse3 :RootMenu

